{"hf7f8b3c5g7643g44f0g8a14gb17a934b8649": ["Prisoner's lost a lot of blood, yer ladyship. Still ain't talkin.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "fcbd40a5-2a76-d696-6492-3fb13492620c"], "h3b4bb79cgc7c0g43a9ga5a8gac76166eb473": ["Tell them to stop cutting him - we need him alive.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "879392b0-caef-5813-b8a9-e21f47355bc7"], "hf5fe9e86g6221g432dgaa09gf80a0e747ae4": ["Break his bones instead. Start with the fingers.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "e25550ec-9492-11b7-cfc6-b22cf4d09890"], "he6a58f9dg8f93g4508gb6efg94aed730c567": ["Raiders are just waiting for the word, mistress. We're ready for anything.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "bd38976b-2aa7-881a-892e-9498ab7f4b48"], "h808124bdg87d1g40a8ga00bgbcd5d229baa6": ["And the prisoner?", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "8760faaf-c171-2f86-e3a4-1dfbcbc35096"], "h7aa4e744gb59dg4d79ga818ge0af13d7c9e9": ["We're still workin' on him.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "989c0c3b-e421-6e94-e712-15a1eb5b1b2a"], "hc5181b9cgdbd8g405fgafdeg2aee63049c9b": ["Sorry to bother you, mistress... got a message from the guards.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "3bb07371-1171-ca39-7f10-97ef2967cd43"], "h52a80990ga43dg429bg8d3ag4744f85189de": ["Yes?", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "5109550a-774c-99cc-0e70-2cd05900468c"], "hfafdd0e6g0e6bg4d8agbbb5g0a3710ca7ba8": ["We got visitors - more True Souls like yerself.", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "a38f9629-bae4-c6a0-493f-93c89d5871d3"], "h88e2734eg9121g4da3g8153g2a6c20be2fb7": ["Interesting. I wasn't expecting guests.", "25721313-0c15-4935-8176-9f134385451b", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "61f1e730-120e-c30b-94f5-7c3da0a08878"], "hcd4464cdg3239g455dg8edfg23a795cc8db8": ["We got visitors. Dunno who they are - mercenaries maybe?", "126e39d1-7c38-453c-888b-4cddce7f3e41", ".\\voicebarks\\Act1\\Goblin\\ADs\\GOB_DrowCommander_AD_WithPatrol.html", "1e0f6edb-3848-4628-7e4c-ce94aba54406"]}